
## CSS FLEX- 2016
-> te ajuta sa gandesti intr-o singura directie ori 
orizontala ori pe verticala.
## CSS native grid a aparut in 2018
Grid- regim de afisare, care poate fi utilizat simultan in doua directii, adica putem imparti elementele pe verticala si orizontala simultan

ASEMANARI:
-> Containerul defineste logica de aliniere a itemelor.
-> Atat flexul cat si gridul au (directia-start, end, spatierea, alinierea, ordinea elementelor"z-index")

DEOSEBIRI:
-> poti prestabilia un schelet ca intr-un tabel(row, cols, suprafete(un sablon de aranjare a elementelor))
-> unitate nou factie- (fr 1fr:2fr)
-> funcii (repeat(...))
-> suprapunerea elementelor ca in pozitionare(item overlap, z-index)
...

Display: CSS NATIVE GRID- MODERN TABLE

-> cols/row
-> container/items
-> start / center / end / spacing / span / reflection
-> order
-> overlap items (z-index)
-> flexible / smart size / alignment
-> unit: fr
-> functions: repeat()
-> gap: distance
-> templating + areas
...



